\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {Dgrammar} (blue tinted): one denoising step applies a full model forward, frontier masking and AIMD unmasking, and incremental \texttt  {extend\_prefix}. \textbf  {DPGrammar} (orange): when a violator is detected at position $c$, \texttt  {dp\_fix\_prefix} jointly rewrites the span $[c,s)$ via Viterbi over top-$K$ tokens before falling back to greedy remasking.}}{4}{figure.caption.13}\protected@file@percent }
